rows.label: tlk70000062_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Check out all this nature! Go
on, take a deep breath. Feels
good, eh? Not like Iira at all.

rows.label: tlk70000062_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Gula's famous for its clear waters
and pristine natural beauty.

rows.label: tlk70000062_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Be careful, though - at the
heart of this land dwell
hordes of strong monsters.

rows.label: tlk70000062_01_msg0004
rows.name:
You'll want to keep an eye out if
you stray too far from the road.
